introduction: Stone Quackers is an American animated television series created by Ben Jones, who also created Cartoon Network's The Problem Solverz. The series revolves around the misadventures of two ducks, Whit and Clay, along with their friends Barf and Dottie, plus the authority Officer Barry and neighborhood kid Bug. This series was premiered October 27, 2014 on FXX as part on their Animation Domination High-Def block.Despite the Animation Domination High-Def block originally airing on Fox, Stone Quackers itself is the first original show to premiere on FXX, that wasn't carried over from another network.
